title: Urbanization in Canada 2018
summary: In general Share of urban population has stayed the same over the Year.
Share of urban population is slightly increasing from 2011 to 2018.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2017 and 2018.
Maximum Share of urban population, about 81.41 was reported at Year 2018
The lowest Share of urban population, of value 81.1 was reported at Year 2011
